ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectNon-Article 5 North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) Medal
PrecisOrder (a) authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the NON-ARTICLE 5 NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION (NATO) MEDAL FOR SERVICE ON OPERATIONS AND ACTIVITIES APPROVED BY THE NORTH ATLANTIC COUNCIL IN RELATION TO AFRICA, in recognition of honourable service; and (b) establishing its order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
